reviewText: What I LIKE about this movie is Rossano Brazzi.  June Allyson does NOTHING for the part.  But I collect Rossano's movies.  The quality of the DVD is great.  I would order from your company again.

Very well made, well acted by the leads. Minor characters were not as alive and convincing as in other movies by Sirk. Extremely good to look at but the story is weak and the final scene a fizzer. Previous to this scene, a magnificent moment when two beautiful and beautifully dressed women enter a swamp.
